title: An Early (but Not Too Early) MVP Conversation | Group Chat
description:
Justin and Rob are joined by J. Kyle Mann to rank their top five MVP candidates and discuss a couple of other guys who could get in the mix.

Hosts: Justin Verrier and Rob Mahoney
Guest: J. Kyle Mann
Associate Producer: Isaiah Blakely
